### 1. Get All Courses (GET)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses

### 2. Create a New Course (POST)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course_name": "CS416 Software Engineering"
}

### 3. Get Assignments for Course 1 (GET)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses/1/assignments

### 4. Create Assignment with Grades (POST)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses/1/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Midterm Exam",
  "grades": [
    { "first_name": "Alice", "middle_name": "", "last_name": "Johnson", "student_id": 1, "score": 92.0 },
    { "first_name": "Bob", "middle_name": "G", "last_name": "Smith", "student_id": 2, "score": 85.5 },
    { "first_name": "Charlie", "middle_name": "", "last_name": "Brown", "student_id": 3, "score": 78.0 },
    { "first_name": "Diana", "middle_name": "M", "last_name": "Lee", "student_id": 4, "score": 95.0 },
    { "first_name": "Eve", "middle_name": "", "last_name": "Davis", "student_id": 5, "score": 60.5 }
  ]
}

### 5. Get Sorted Students — All (GET)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/students

### 6. Get Sorted Students — Filtered by Assignment (GET)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/students?assignment_id=1

### 7. Get Average — All (GET)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/average

### 8. Get Average — Filtered by Assignment (GET)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/average?assignment_id=1

### 9. Add a Single Student (POST)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Isaac",
  "middle_name": "G",
  "last_name": "Smith",
  "student_id": 6,
  "score": 85.5
}